		"Id": "vehicledef_DEMOLISHER_PAI",
		"Name": "Periphery Demolisher",
		"Details": "Tall, squat, and using four treads, the Demolisher has a well-earned reputation as one of the most deadly vehicles on the battlefield.  Developed in the periphery as an all range battlemech substitute.  Unlike most Demolisher variants of the Inner Sphere, the Periphery Demolisher gives up its hard to source Autocannons for easier to produce and longer ranged Howitzers.  The Periphery Demolisher carries a pair of Howitzer/12s with 8 tons of ammunition.  With the extra mass and space saved, the Periphery Demolisher also has one each of a Gyrojet 20 and RocketLauncher 20 on its front glacis.  It utilizes 10 tons of armor for protection, and the I.C.E. motor allows for a cruising speed 32.4kph.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Tracked: High traction, agile turning.</color></b>\n\n \n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 3/5 Hex: 90/150 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       216     40\n<b>Left</b>         150     40\n<b>Right</b>       150     40\n<b>Rear</b>        100     40\n<b>Turret</b>      200     40\n\n<b>Total</b>      816    200\n",
		"Icon": "Demolisher"
	},
